ETI = Enterprise Technology Integration.
DS = Data Science.
ICE = Information Compliance and Ethics.
AI = Artificial Intelligence.
GA = General Arts.
GH = General Humanities.
GS = General Social and Behavioral Sciences.
GN = General Natural Science.
GHW = General Health and Wellness.
GQ = General Quantification.
GWS = General Writing and Speaking.
INTER-D = Inter domain.
